The paper focuses on semantic segmentation for object parsing, which is a common task in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed architecture also involves attention mechanisms and context integration, which are popular topics in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper evaluates the efficiency of the proposed method, which is relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) and natural language processing (cs.CL) fields.
